data.description: Step into history with this captivating 2br/1ba home that exudes timeless charm and character. This gem is nestled in the charming town of Moscow TN. This home offers a connection to the past while being conveniently close to Collierville TN. Embrace the sense of community and relish in the stories this neighborhood has witnessed over the years. This home provides a unique opportunity for those who appreciate the beauty of a bygone era and want to infuse their own story into its walls.
